name: PRJKT SUCCUBUS
description:
A stray coding error in the execution of PRJKTNEON unlocked the containment vessel of PRJKT SUCCUBUS, a demonic entity experimented on in order to gain the secrets of immortality for the powerful. 

Due to her impossible regenerative ability upon consumption of human flesh, PRJKT SUCCUBUS was repeatedly tortured and experimented upon in order to perfect the techno-enhancements that for the foundation of the AVATARS.

Finally awake and finding herself unshackled, this tech-enhanced demon is hunting immortals to return the pain they gave her a hundred times over.
